STEPS to run the project

1. clone the project to your local machine
2. run npm i
3. start mongoDB Server


API Details

1. 
http://localhost:3000/register
Method - POST
{
    "email": "tanveer.singh1@inc3.com",
    "password": "Admin@123",
    "confirmPassword": "Admin@123"
}


2. http://localhost:3000/login
Method - POST
{
    "email": "tanveer.singh1@inc3.com",
    "password": "Admin@123"
}



-- Protected API's (provide access token in request header) -------
   
http://localhost:3000/user/profile
Method - POST
{ 
    "name": "Tanveer Singh 2",
    "profileImage": "",
    "aboutUs": "sample text"
}




http://localhost:3000/video
Method - POST
{
  video: <add video to upload>
}




http://localhost:3000/video?videoId=67b9a900c4d56e6c446c967c
Method - GET
Returns the video in chunks as response.
